### Register User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}


### Login User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

